flowchart TD
    Start((Start Booking)) --> Search[Browse Therapists List]
    
    Search --> Filter[Filter by Specialty / Price / Rating]
    Filter --> ViewProfile[View Therapist Profile & Bio]
    
    ViewProfile --> SelectSlot[Select Date and Time Slot]
    
    SelectSlot --> CheckSQL{Is Slot Still \n Available?}
    
    CheckSQL -- No --> Conflict[Show Error: Slot Just Taken]
    Conflict --> SelectSlot
    
    CheckSQL -- Yes --> SessionType{Choose Session \n Type}
    
    SessionType -- Online --> VideoLink[Generate Meeting Link Placeholder]
    SessionType -- Offline --> ClinicInfo[Show Clinic Address & Location]
    
    VideoLink --> Payment[Payment Gateway / Insurance]
    ClinicInfo --> Payment
    
    Payment --> PayStatus{Payment \n Successful?}
    
    PayStatus -- No --> Retry[Retry or Change Method]
    Retry --> Payment
    
    PayStatus -- Yes --> DBUpdate[SQL: Update Slot Status to 'Reserved']
    
    DBUpdate --> Notify[Send Confirmation SMS / Email]
    Notify --> Dashboard[Add to User Upcoming Sessions]
    Dashboard --> End((End))